RACE.FOOTNOTES: SPIRIT OF POWER tracked in the two path around the first turn and was in the three path down the backstretch, was cued to range up in the three path around the far turn, floated out to the eight path while taking aim entering the lane, swept past a pair of inner foes into the final furlong, and held off a late charging outer foe to win. HOT BOTTOM GIRL set the pace along the inside, was coaxed around the far turn and in the two path at the top of the stretch, but yielded entering the final furlong. RIA FORMOSA was in the two path around the first turn and rated in the four path down the backside, was urged from the six path turning into the stretch, but was no factor. STARSHIP BABE stalked in the two path down the backstretch, was ridden around the far turn, but faded entering the lane. POMONA'S BULLET trailed in the five path down the backstretch, was driven in the four path around the far turn, but was no menace.
